summary: I feel like the peak internet for me was some time around 2004.  The internet felt balanced, and I was happy with my relationship with it.  Sure, I probably spent more time than I should have on the internet, but at least I wasn't carrying it around with me...
title: Adding a Little Friction to My Computing
